    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, i'm looking at some specs for a new batch of high-end Egyptian cotton linens. The client is asking for a super-fine weave to ensure the fabric is extremely dense and tight. What's the best way to describe the relationship between thread count and weave density in a technical report to show how the tightness of the weave provides a more substantial barrier?",
